      <div class="section-header reveal">
        <p class="section-label">GEO Pricing</p>
        <h2>GEO pricing &mdash; published in full</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="pillar-prose reveal">
        <p>We publish our fees. A GEO agency that publishes its pricing is also publishing the labour math behind it &mdash; which is the point. The SG market range for GEO retainers is currently S$2,500-S$15,000 per month depending on scope and how many AI platforms you&rsquo;re monitoring. Anything quoted under S$2,000/month is almost always traditional SEO with "AI" or "GEO" added to the package name. Schema implementation done correctly on a 30-page site is 8-12 hours. Answer-engine content is 4-6 hours per page. Citation building takes outreach hours that don&rsquo;t compress with software.</p>
      </div>
